== 經歷 ==
=== 出道前 ===
Ladies' Code五位成員活躍多個領域，使她們出道前已獲得了一定的人氣。

[[權梨世|梨世]]於2009年參加了第53屆韓國小姐得到國際冬季競賽大獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://biz.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=20130402000672 |script-title=ko:권리세 미스코리아 시절 “미코진 옆에서도 빛나” |date=April 2, 2013 |publisher=The Korea Herald |access-date=October 26, 2014 |language=ko}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.donga.com/rel/3/all/20140907/66268457/1 |script-title=ko:가족 곁에서 숨 거둔 미소천사 권리세, “비보에 목메어 눈물만...” |date=September 7, 2014 |website=donga.com |publisher=Dong-a |access-date=October 26, 2014 |language=ko}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web |title=Kim Ju-Ri Wins Miss Korea 2009 |url=http://www.koreanbeacon.com/2009/07/08/kim-ju-ri-wins-miss-korea-2009/ |date=July 8, 2009 |publisher=Korean Beacon |access-date=April 28, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140112031622/http://www.koreanbeacon.com/2009/07/08/kim-ju-ri-wins-miss-korea-2009/ |archive-date=January 12, 2014}}</ref> 。此後於2011年參加節目[[偉大的誕生|偉大的誕生]]，可惜只於12強止步<ref name="hankyung">{{cite web |url=http://www.hankyung.com/news/app/newsview.php?aid=2011060877797 |script-title=ko:데이비드오 - 권리세 우결 출연 확정 |date=June 8, 2011 |website=Hankyung.com |publisher=The Korea Economic Daily |access-date=October 26, 2014 |language=ko}}</ref>，同年與同為[[偉大的誕生|偉大的誕生]]出身的[[吳世勛_(韓國歌手)|吳志勛]]出演了[[我們結婚了|我們結婚了]]，組成物理夫婦，使其成為Ladies' Code出道時知名度最高的成員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/285/kwon-ri-sae-david-oh-couple-to-leave-we-got-married |title=Kwon Ri Sae-David Oh Couple To Leave ′We Got Married′ |last=Lee |first=Kyung-nam |date=September 6, 2011 |work=CJ E&M enewsWorld |publisher=Mwave |access-date=October 26, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027050122/http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/285/kwon-ri-sae-david-oh-couple-to-leave-we-got-married |archive-date=October 27, 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref> Rise later signed on with [[KeyEast|KeyEast]] before switching agencies in 2013.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/26233/kwon-ri-sae-joins-polaris-ent |title='The Great Birth's Kwon Ri Sae Moves From Key East to Polaris Entertainment |last=Ho |first=Stewart |date=January 11, 2011 |work=CJ E&M enewsWorld |publisher=Mwave |access-date=October 27, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028052618/http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/26233/kwon-ri-sae-joins-polaris-ent |archive-date=October 28, 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。

EunB之前是FNC Entertainment的練習生，她是[[AOA|AOA]]的原始陣容。然而，她在小組出道前離開了公司，因為她覺得自己需要更多的練習生經驗<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.koreaboo.com/news/female-idols-celebrate-late-ladies-code-eunbs-birthday-instagram/ | title=Female idols celebrate the late Ladies' Code EunB's birthday on Instagram| date=November 24, 2015}}</ref>。 

昭政於出道前參加[[好聲音|Voice Korea]]，其充滿感染力的歌聲獲得導師激賞，以四轉（所有導師轉身）的成績晉級，最終止步於全國8強<ref>{{cite web |url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2013030708592633388 |script-title=ko:권리세·이소정 新걸그룹 "실력파 평가가 목표"(인터뷰) |date=March 7, 2013 |last=Gil |first=Hye-seong |publisher=Star News |access-date=September 15, 2014 |language=ko}}</ref>。

Ashley出道前經常上傳舞蹈影片於自己的[[YouTube|YouTube]]频道，後為圓音樂夢從韓人密集的[[纽约|紐約]][[皇后區|皇后區]]回到韓國，曾為[[Cube娛樂|Cube娛樂]]練習生。

===2013年===
2月24日，各成員的預告影片釋出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvdaily.asiae.co.kr/read.php3?aid=1361326711469005010 |script-title=ko:'보코 출신' 이소정, 권리세 걸그룹 합류 "3월 전격데뷔" |date=February 20, 2013 |publisher=TV Daily |access-date=September 10, 2014 |language=ko}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/29638/the-voice-of-korea-meets-the-great-birth-in-polaris-entertainments-upcoming-girl-group |title=′Voice of Korea′s′ Lee So Jung to Join ′The Great Birth′s′ Kwon Ri Sae′s Group |last=Choi |first=Eun-hwa |date=February 20, 2013 |work=CJ E&M enewsWorld |publisher=MWave |access-date=September 10, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060819/http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/29638/the-voice-of-korea-meets-the-great-birth-in-polaris-entertainments-upcoming-girl-group |archive-date=March 4, 2016 |url-status=dead }}</ref> 。

3月7日，Ladies' Code首張迷你專輯《CODE #01 壞女孩》全線發行<ref name="debut">{{cite web |url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/30826/ladies-code-releases-new-mv |title=[Video] Ladies Code Debuts as Bad Girls in New MV |last=Hong |first=Grace |date=March 7, 2013 |work=CJ E&M enewsWorld |publisher=MWave |access-date=September 10, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505173716/http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/30826/ladies-code-releases-new-mv |archive-date=May 5, 2016 |url-status=dead }}</ref> ，同日於[[M!_Countdown|M! Countdown]]中正式出道。完成《壞女孩（Bad Girl）》的宣傳後，Ladies' Code開始錄製新曲，原定於七月回歸，但因成員Zuny右腳受傷，公司決定延遲回歸<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2013070912220596565 |script-title=ko:레이디스코드 주니, 연습 중 '앗!'... 무릎 부상으로 컴백 '무기한 연기' |last=Yi |first=Geum-jun |date=July 9, 2013 |publisher=Asia Economics |access-date=October 30, 2014 |language=ko}}</ref><ref name="hateyou">{{cite web |url=http://www.mtvk.com/blog-posts/ladies-code-goes-horror-for-pre-release-hate-you/ |title=Ladies Code Goes Horror for Pre-Release "Hate You" |last=Smith |first=Corynn |date=August 6, 2013 |publisher=MTV K |access-date=September 10, 2014}}</ref> 。

7月末，Ladies' Code公開了第二張迷你專輯先行曲《Hate you》的預告影片，短短的預告中，以娃娃人偶們為主角，散發一股詭譎的氣氛。

8月6日，先行曲《Hate you》正式發表。〈Hate you〉這首歌與製作出道曲〈壞女孩（Bad Girl）〉的Super Changddai再次合作。不斷重複的歌詞「Hate You」、「Love You」讓人留下深刻印象，MV也給人毛骨悚然的感覺。經紀公司Polaris Entertainment表示：「Ladies' Code將透過與〈壞女孩〉完全不同風格的〈Hate you〉，讓大家看到她們更成熟的魅力」。雖然Ladies' Code沒有登上音樂節目宣傳，〈Hate you〉仍獲得亮眼的成績，曾在Bugs的排行榜拿下實時一位。

9月，Ladies' Code以第二張迷你專輯《CODE #02 Pretty! Pretty!》回歸<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2013082110371366603 |script-title=ko:레이디스 코드, 통통 튀는 매력 입었다... '예뻐예뻐'로 9月 컴백 |last=Lee |first=Kim-jun |date=August 21, 2013 |publisher=Asia Economics |access-date=September 10, 2014 |language=ko}}</ref>，形象較為活潑和俏皮。主打歌〈Pretty! Pretty!〉也相當輕快，讓粉絲看到她們與過去不同的面貌。這次回歸得到非常多的支持及推薦，如[[Wonder_Girls|Wonder Girls]]的[[閔先藝|先藝]]、[[2PM|2PM]]的[[Nichkhun|Nichkhun]]、[[金閔俊|Jun. K]]等。

